13:00.396 --> 13:03.022
You have to help me.

13:03.116 --> 13:06.284
You have to help me right now.

13:06.435 --> 13:08.011
Should just be
another couple minutes.

13:08.029 --> 13:09.954
KID 2:
Dad, Tyson spilled
fruit punch on me.

13:10.106 --> 13:11.122
KID:
No, I didn't.

13:11.315 --> 13:13.291
KID 2:
Dad!

13:13.460 --> 13:15.418
(sighs)

13:24.087 --> 13:25.637
Meg, there you are.

13:25.830 --> 13:28.122
-Look, I wanted
to apologize and...
