have liked this week,

19:54.419 --> 19:55.300
so we didn't get
to do everything

19:55.453 --> 19:57.086
we wanted to with my hands.

19:57.188 --> 19:59.680
So, here's a supercut of me
having a little fun around town.

19:59.741 --> 20:02.107
We like it a lot.
We hope you will, too.

